        <Parent_String>portland cement [300010377], cement by composition or origin [300010363], cement (construction material) [300010362], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
